ReviewText: For many years I've used Gold Blend.  Then I discovered NESCAFÉ Gold Blend Crema.  This is the most delicious instant coffee I have ever bought, and I have  over 40 years 'experience' of drinking coffee, different brands and different products.  Yes it is as described.... smooth, rounded and creamy.  But better than that it IS the best coffee to use in team tea kittys or for company guests and clients.  Why?  because it is a quality drink, far superior to ordinary Gold Blend.  Looks good when served with a distinctive 'top', has a rich coffee taste but without  sharpness.  This is the only coffee that I've served to company guests and clients that is universally finished to the last drop.   Now that says something.
Title: Delicious - best all round choice.

ReviewText: My cupboard is full of Nescafe products, Azeera Americans for everyday, Expression for my other half and for treats and after dinner.....Crema!!!!  This instant coffee is, as are they all, everything it promises to be.  It is rich, very smooth but tasty.  It is like liquid velvet.  I hate coffee which has no flavour but this is a real taste experience!!!  Every evening, after dinner, when the chores are complete, this coffee is my secret vice.  It makes me feel good and I love it!!!!  It is for special guests only as I love it too much to share but, those chosen ones I have converted!!!!  Never stop making this Nescafe!!!!  It really is the dog's wotsits!!!!!!
Title: Sheer Decadence In A Jar

ReviewText: I bought a jar of Nescafe Gold Crema around 5/6 weeks ago.  The coffee has a distinctive, smooth, light and creamy taste.  It isn't as strong as other coffee brands that i've tasted, which was an added bonus.  The value of the coffee was quite good, when I compare it to other brands I have tried.  A friend came over to visit and I made her a cup of this coffee.  She commented on how nice it tasted, said she had never heard of it or tried it before and then said she'd be going out to buy a jar of it.  In general people never comment on coffee, but this made a lasting impression.  I doubt I'd go back to another brand/type of coffee now I've tried it.  It is excellent, in my opinion.
Title: Nescafe Gold Crema

ReviewText: I bought this as an alternative to my normal Nescafe a few weeks ago and I'm so glad I tried it. I love the velvety taste of this coffee, which isn't bitter, just smooth and rich in taste. We don't drink a lot of coffee at home, but like a good quality instant coffee and this ticks all the boxes. I warm the milk first, add the Crema and a sugar to taste, then pour on boiling water, stirring all the while. It has a lovely rich aroma that makes my taste buds tingle and for the price, it's an excellent cup of coffee. If you like a smooth, creamy coffee without paying premium prices, you should try this!
Title: Deliciously creamy!

ReviewText: I had the pleasure of consuming this new coffee yesterday. I haven't been allowed caffeine for over a year, so this really hit the spot! The crema was fantastic, I couldn't believe this was an instant coffee! I'm looking forward to enjoying this on the balcony every morning.
Title: Delicious taste! Can't wait to keep drinking it :)

ClientResponses.Response: Hi, thanks very much for letting us know your thoughts on the new recipe.
